findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeInReward() and _getCurrentSupply() may abort with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long excluded addresses list.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to change tax and liquidity fee, maximum transaction amount, exclude from fee or reward, activate/deactivate swap and liquify process, lock and unlock, which can be exploited even after ownership renouncement.
